grations exist for Typesafe Config, log4j, log4j2, and slf4j, but they are not required for meaningful core utility/JNDI coverage.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0934c9e775115166016a3ec3e3f5448193841ea381da0ac43b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3476, "output": 822, "cacheRead": 32768, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 37066, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782498266866, "responseId": "resp_0934c9e775115166016a3ec3db5114819380368ddec5c49f2a"}}
